{"tid":1462320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣總統指示各部會 對港人啟動「人道救援」","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:37.000Z","uid":296328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"320769106ccb6e6d1dd93f163d9720af14f68c28","tid":1462320,"uid":296328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"節錄於 台灣 <span style=\"color: green;\">民主進步黨</span> Facebook Page<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n【強烈譴責 <span style=\"color: red;\">北京</span>與港府跨越道德底線的暴力作為】<br />\n　<br />\n關閉機場，切斷對外交通，一向是獨裁政權動用強勢武力的前兆，港人正在經歷的，一場沒有戒嚴的戒嚴，是一場尚未出動坦克的血腥鎮壓，身為自由民主社會的一員，台灣不可能漠視<span style=\"color: red;\">北京</span>與港府的暴力作為。<br />\n　<br />\n香港的朋友，我們和你站在一起，<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡英文</span>總統及政府相關單位也明示，會以人道救援的方式，給予個案上的協助。<br />\n　<br />\n香港加油，我們也要守住台灣。<br />\n<br />\n＃警察還眼 ＃過分武力 ＃反送中<br />\n-<br />\nFacebook Link: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Z0R4Nw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0R4Nw&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c07f443f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Z0R4Nw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xktrwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xktrwW.jpg&h=2995388f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b41c6b2298be7185404452797a7c379c125903f4","tid":1462320,"uid":296328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"447cf7847cab8338ad804e41aad08212304ad77a","tid":1462320,"uid":296328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c29e3427a2900284e8e4bccd49ac5af944a85a9f","tid":1462320,"uid":211790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}